e in that zone including all the way to zone edge.  The zone canyon to BW is clear of mobs usually too, but dont care for terrain there myself.  After you hit 45 or so try the giant fort in BW.  You may not be able to take ancients alone, but there are usually enuf groups there that you can choose the mobs you can handle and often get oportunity go get in groups as well.  Once you get IC at lvl49 and Pillar of Frost at 51, the devistating damage that Ice does to mobs in BW will make it hard to leave there since you will be killing at will.  I admit that level 40 was a little annoying for me too when I could not grab a group... &lt;Sigh&gt; too powerful for Overthere and not quite able to Own the dreadlands.   <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><TABLE WIDTH=240 BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0>
